                    <Bold>
                        3. Entity1
                    </Bold>
                </Italic>
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph>
                Entity1 is the name of a SQL command that has been defined in the SQL Cmds tab. 
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph FontSize="14pt" >
                <Italic>
                    <Bold>
                        4. Relationship
                    </Bold>
                </Italic>
            </Paragraph>
            <Paragraph>
                Relationship is not used.
            </Paragraph>
